reviewText: Interesting and inspiring, but kind of slow. Could have been edited more tightly.

I am moved beyond words by this story.  I have been drumming (totally as an amateur) for several years, so the djembe caught my eye on the cover.  I knew there would be much more to the story, and there is more and more and more.  Inspiring, hopeful, sad, life changing.  You just have to see it.
